",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"CollectionPage\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/wichita-ks#webpage\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks in Wichita, KS\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Discover Barks & Brews indoor park and multiple off-leash areas in Wichita, KS. The ultimate guide to dog-friendly ICT.\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/cities/wichita-ks\\\",\\\"image\\\":\\\"/images/cities/wichita-ks/hero.webp\\\",\\\"datePublished\\\":\\\"2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\\\",\\\"dateModified\\\":\\\"2026-02-06T03:05:23.338Z\\\",\\\"publisher\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Indoor Dog Park\\\",\\\"logo\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ImageObject\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/images/logo/logo-512.png\\\"}},\\\"about\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"City\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Wichita, KS\\\"},\\\"containsPlace\\\":[]}\"}}],false,[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"FAQPage\\\",\\\"mainEntity\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Does Wichita have an indoor dog park?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Yes, Barks & Brews is a popular spot combining an indoor/outdoor dog park with a bar. It is great for socializing year-round.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"How many dog parks are in Wichita?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Wichita has several, including Chapin Dog Park (formerly Herman Hill), Meridian Dog Park, and Harrison Dog Park, offering plenty of variety.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Is Naftzger Park dog-friendly?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Yes, Naftzger Park downtown features a dedicated dog run with artificial turf, making it a convenient stop for urban dwellers.\\\"}}]}\"}}],[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Wichita\\\"}]}\"}}],[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}],[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"title\":\"Map & Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"planning-essentials\",\"title\":\"Planning Essentials\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"expert-tips\",\"title\":\"Expert Advice\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-directory\",\"title\":\"Full Directory\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"owner-cta\",\"title\":\"Owner & Franchise\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"faq-section\",\"title\":\"FAQs\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"title\":\"More Resources\",\"level\":1}]}],[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],\"$L6\"]}],\"$L7\",\"$L8\",\"$undefined\",\"$L9\",\"$La\",\"$Lb\",\"$Lc\"]}],\"$Ld\"]}]}],\"$Le\",\"$Lf\",\"$L10\",\"$L11\",\"$L12\",\"$L13\",\"$undefined\",\"$L14\",\"$L15\",false,\"$L16\",\"$L17\"]}],\"$L18\",\"$L19\"],null,\"$L1a\"]}],\"loading\":null,\"isPartial\":false}\n6:[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Wichita\"}]\n7:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"City spotlight\"}]\n8:[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Indoor Dog Park In Wichita\"}]\n9:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Discover Barks & Brews indoor park and multiple off-leash areas in Wichita, KS. The ultimate guide to dog-friendly ICT.\"}]\na:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Wichita has embraced the modern dog ownership lifestyle with Barks & Brews, an indoor/outdoor dog park and bar that solves the problem of Kansas weather. This facility allows dogs to play in a climate-controlled environment while owners socialize. The city also maintains several excellent municipal dog parks, including those at Chapin Park and Meridian Park, ensuring access to off-leash space across the city. Naftzger Park downtown even includes a turf dog run for urban residents. We are constantly looking for new \",[\"$\",\"$L5\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/partners\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"partners\"}],null,\" to expand our network in the region.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"The Arkansas River path offers miles of scenic walking right through the heart of the city. Wichita's diverse neighborhoods, from the historic Delano district to the college hill area, are walkable and pet-friendly. The community is active, with many dog-centric events throughout the year. With a mix of innovative private businesses and solid public infrastructure, Wichita is a fantastic city for dogs. Check our \",[\"$\",\"$L5\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/blog\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"blog\"}],null,\" for upcoming event announcements.\"]}]]}]\nb:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}]\nc:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]\nd:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L1b\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/c